{"tid":2175545,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"人民日報評論：「蘋果日報」很可能是具相當危險性的政治組織","createTime":"2020-08-26T14:00:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T14:02:52.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e078432a693059aba77a4e9538528b65f80228b8","tid":2175545,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T14:00:34.000Z","msg":"官方人民日報在&ldquo;人民銳評&rdquo;欄目，發表評論文章，點名指蘋果日報，並非只是反對派的&ldquo;政治傳單&rdquo;、亂港勢力的&ldquo;文宣機器&rdquo;，本身很可能就是一個具有相當危險性的&ldquo;政治組織&rdquo;。 <br />\n<br />\n文章批評蘋果日報在香港第三波疫情來到時，關心的只是能不能借此製造對立、吸引眼球。<br />\n<br />\n凡是政府推出的抗疫舉措，一律攻擊、抹黑；凡是大陸支援香港的行動，一律污蔑、中傷，所作所為，就是為撕裂社會、消解共識、阻撓抗疫，好&ldquo;借亂謀利&rdquo;、&ldquo;借疫生財&rdquo;。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2354372\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2354372&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhatr7zmW0KSjJ%2FkJHMgTQKA%2BU%3D&h=0607291a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2354372</a>"},{"pid":"c7df7616649c0dae7e23c3a851b22eba24c8b02d","tid":2175545,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T14:02:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"19971f253963adc923b7c558a59ab9636c911f90","tid":2175545,"uid":226466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T14:02:52.000Z","msg":"以為老衲<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}